  This release includes support for the following DLC:
  
  - Dungeon Maestro Grimoire Pack

  Update changes:

  Bug Fixes
  - Fixed a bug that would cause The Elder Dragon to not be affected
    by the High Stakes Challenge
  - Fixed a bug that would cause Mage hosts to don't move properly
    on clients

  Improvements and Optimizations
  - Added some new effect at The Log Simulator Ride.
  - Dungeonland will recognize your system language for initial
    language setting
  - Added DMMode victory and defeat voice lines
  - Fixed a few sound issues regarding the bosses and player VOs



  Instructions:

  - Install using the Setup.exe ( point to your installation folder
    if required )
